      "content": "i don't know... i just wonder if there's actually any dignity in sticking around to watch it all burn. if the end is inevitable, it feels less like \"defiance\" and more like just... unnecessarily prolonging the suffering. like, why stay for a tragedy that's already scripted? it feels like the only logical thing to do is just opt out before things get even worse.",
